c: 12
v: 109
t: "Ndipo Ife sitinatumizepo iwe usanadze, wina kupatula anthu amene tinawatsogolera kuchokera pakati pa anthu a m’mizinda. Kodi iwo sanayende padziko ndi kuona zimene zidawachitikira amene adalipo kale? Ndipo, ndithudi, moyo umene uli nkudza ndi wabwino kwa anthu amene amaopa Mulungu ndipo amamumvera Iye. Kodi mulibe nzeru"